                  <label>Principal property involved and scope of problem</label>
                  <p>Due to the fact that <person role="1" wra-ref="503463">Mr. Hachiya</person> has been a minor, has held up the property management of the <orgName project-ref="JAIFRP-org-0058">Columbia Hotel</orgName> with the <orgName project-ref="JAIFRP-org-0031">Commonwealth Inc.</orgName> through Atty <person role="2" project-ref="JAIFRP-00096">E.J. McAlear</person> First Natl Bank Bldg. Hillsboro Ore. - <person role="1" wra-ref="503463">Ted</person> will be of age tomorrow (<date when="1942-06-23">June 23</date>) and atty <person role="2" project-ref="JAIFRP-00096">McAlear</person> should be set up by the court as Trustee - or have power of atty for <person role="1" wra-ref="503463">Mr. Hachiya</person> before <orgName project-ref="JAIFRP-org-0031">Commonwealth</orgName> will take over management. The inventory is rather incomplete and should be made over - Some check should be made of the personal belongings of several Japanese stored at this Hotel.</p>
